[
  {
    "start": 0.0,
    "end": 2.0,
    "text": "Who's that Pokemon?"
  },
  {
    "start": 2.0,
    "end": 4.0,
    "text": "It's Pikachu!"
  },
  {
    "start": 10.0,
    "end": 14.0,
    "text": "Hey guys, so today I'm going to show you how to make your very own Pikachu cake."
  },
  {
    "start": 14.0,
    "end": 21.0,
    "text": "Now the icing colors you're going to be needing for this tutorial are yellow, ugly pink, ugly red, white, and black."
  },
  {
    "start": 21.0,
    "end": 27.0,
    "text": "So to get the perfect image of Pikachu, I went on the internet and just found whichever face that I liked."
  },
  {
    "start": 27.0,
    "end": 33.0,
    "text": "So what I did was I took my iPad and I tried to match up the size of the cake with the size of the picture."
  },
  {
    "start": 33.0,
    "end": 38.0,
    "text": "So just about... there."
  },
  {
    "start": 38.0,
    "end": 46.0,
    "text": "So that when I start outlining his eyes, I can sort of match up the distance from the top of the cake to the top of the cake here."
  },
  {
    "start": 46.0,
    "end": 50.0,
    "text": "And then I just want to start outlining the eyes."
  },
  {
    "start": 50.0,
    "end": 53.0,
    "text": "Pokemon facts! Scientific name."
  },
  {
    "start": 53.0,
    "end": 56.0,
    "text": "So Pikachu's scientific name is um..."
  },
  {
    "start": 57.0,
    "end": 61.0,
    "text": "Pikalicious Chu."
  },
  {
    "start": 61.0,
    "end": 64.0,
    "text": "Which in Navajo means..."
  },
  {
    "start": 64.0,
    "end": 66.0,
    "text": "Heavy yellow sneeze."
  },
  {
    "start": 66.0,
    "end": 68.0,
    "text": "Hot Chu."
  },
  {
    "start": 68.0,
    "end": 72.0,
    "text": "Now using the 18 star tip, we're going to start icing the cake on the top."
  },
  {
    "start": 72.0,
    "end": 74.0,
    "text": "Ah, that's going to be good."
  },
  {
    "start": 74.0,
    "end": 75.0,
    "text": "Location."
  },
  {
    "start": 75.0,
    "end": 81.0,
    "text": "Uh, if you're looking for Pikachu, um, you can primarily find them in my basement."
  },
  {
    "start": 81.0,
    "end": 85.0,
    "text": "I kill them with rat traps because I always find them eating my dog food."
  },
  {
    "start": 85.0,
    "end": 86.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 86.0,
    "end": 87.0,
    "text": "So right when you get there,"
  },
  {
    "start": 87.0,
    "end": 91.0,
    "text": "to the eyes of Pikachu, you're going to want to switch to the black icing."
  },
  {
    "start": 91.0,
    "end": 93.0,
    "text": "Just start rounding the eyes."
  },
  {
    "start": 93.0,
    "end": 94.0,
    "text": "Oh, I don't want to fuck this up."
  },
  {
    "start": 94.0,
    "end": 95.0,
    "text": "Please don't fuck this up."
  },
  {
    "start": 99.0,
    "end": 101.0,
    "text": "It's okay. I'm the only one eating this fucking cake."
  },
  {
    "start": 101.0,
    "end": 103.0,
    "text": "Who discovered them?"
  },
  {
    "start": 103.0,
    "end": 108.0,
    "text": "Uh, Pikachu was actually discovered by J.K. Denim."
  },
  {
    "start": 108.0,
    "end": 109.0,
    "text": "Who is me."
  },
  {
    "start": 109.0,
    "end": 112.0,
    "text": "Uh, and I discovered him in my basement."
  },
  {
    "start": 112.0,
    "end": 116.0,
    "text": "Then we're going to take the red and we're going to do the mouth."
  },
  {
    "start": 116.0,
    "end": 120.0,
    "text": "We're going to take the ugly pink and we're going to do the bottom of the mouth."
  },
  {
    "start": 120.0,
    "end": 123.0,
    "text": "Ha, that looks so cute."
  },
  {
    "start": 123.0,
    "end": 125.0,
    "text": "Oh my god, this is adorable."
  },
  {
    "start": 125.0,
    "end": 126.0,
    "text": "Diet."
  },
  {
    "start": 126.0,
    "end": 131.0,
    "text": "Pikachu's diet primarily consists of dog food, obviously."
  },
  {
    "start": 131.0,
    "end": 140.0,
    "text": "Uh, chicken sprinkled with rat poison, avocados sprinkled with rat poison, and apples because apples are delicious."
  },
  {
    "start": 140.0,
    "end": 142.0,
    "text": "I hate those little rascals."
  },
  {
    "start": 142.0,
    "end": 144.0,
    "text": "So when you get to his cheeks, you're going to switch over to the bright red."
  },
  {
    "start": 144.0,
    "end": 147.0,
    "text": "And you're going to fill those circles in."
  },
  {
    "start": 147.0,
    "end": 148.0,
    "text": "Reproduction."
  },
  {
    "start": 148.0,
    "end": 151.0,
    "text": "So, Pikachu's reproduce rapidly."
  },
  {
    "start": 151.0,
    "end": 155.0,
    "text": "They're always in my basement doing it to Marvin Gaye music."
  },
  {
    "start": 155.0,
    "end": 158.0,
    "text": "And I'm like, come on guys, come on."
  },
  {
    "start": 158.0,
    "end": 159.0,
    "text": "Ooh, kill him."
  },
  {
    "start": 159.0,
    "end": 161.0,
    "text": "He looks so cute."
  },
  {
    "start": 161.0,
    "end": 162.0,
    "text": "Oh my god."
