  {
    "start": 162.0,
    "end": 163.0,
    "text": "Oh."
  },
  {
    "start": 163.0,
    "end": 165.0,
    "text": "Now we're going to fill in the rest of the top with a yellow icing."
  },
  {
    "start": 165.0,
    "end": 167.0,
    "text": "Behavior."
  },
  {
    "start": 167.0,
    "end": 168.0,
    "text": "Behavior."
  },
  {
    "start": 168.0,
    "end": 170.0,
    "text": "Pikachu's behavior is very erratic."
  },
  {
    "start": 170.0,
    "end": 171.0,
    "text": "Sometimes they're really cute."
  },
  {
    "start": 171.0,
    "end": 173.0,
    "text": "Like when you put them on a cake, they're kind of really cute."
  },
  {
    "start": 173.0,
    "end": 174.0,
    "text": "But this one."
  },
  {
    "start": 174.0,
    "end": 177.0,
    "text": "Then they're kind of assholes because they eat all the food."
  },
  {
    "start": 177.0,
    "end": 178.0,
    "text": "Yeah, hold on."
  },
  {
    "start": 178.0,
    "end": 179.0,
    "text": "I'm just going to grab."
  },
  {
    "start": 184.0,
    "end": 186.0,
    "text": "I'm going to fucking kill you."
  },
  {
    "start": 186.0,
    "end": 187.0,
    "text": "What kind of shit is that?"
  },
  {
    "start": 187.0,
    "end": 188.0,
    "text": "Ba-bam."
  },
  {
    "start": 188.0,
    "end": 189.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "start": 189.0,
    "end": 193.0,
    "text": "So on the side of the cake, I thought I'd make it a little bit more interesting than just plain yellow."
  },
  {
    "start": 193.0,
    "end": 196.0,
    "text": "And I put Pikachu's type, which is thunder."
  },
  {
    "start": 196.0,
    "end": 197.0,
    "text": "Ta-da."
  },
  {
    "start": 197.0,
    "end": 199.0,
    "text": "Well, I hope you guys enjoyed this."
  },
  {
    "start": 199.0,
    "end": 201.0,
    "text": "I'll see you very soon."
